1.4 Describe the risks that might impact digital projects – what causes digital
projects to fail? Why?
Failure to plan/structure the project adequately.
Breakdown of communication. Failure to assess and monitor progress. 

https://www.pmi.org/learning/library/seven-causes-project-failure-initiate-recovery-7195
